A large, brown, leather-clad automaton, holding a worn book, stands next to a small, blue, pig-shaped car in a dimly lit, rustic workshop. The automaton sighs and stretches, looking downwards. A small, orange-skinned character, wearing a pilot helmet adorned with colorful gadgets, pops up from the pig car, initially looking sleepy. The character lets out a big yawn, then slowly blinks awake, a smile spreading across its face. It then eagerly asks, <S>Ovi mode test time?<E> Turning towards the automaton, it excitedly calls out, <S>Gaga! Hit second gear!<E> As it gestures, beginning to say <S>Piggy is a universe now?<E>, the automaton's hand abruptly drops the book. 

<AUDCAP>A soft sigh, a loud yawn, a high-pitched, enthusiastic child's voice, a sudden thud<ENDAUDCAP>
Audio: A soft sigh, a loud yawn, a high-pitched, enthusiastic child's voice, a sudden thud.
